items.headline: The First Step To Becoming The Best Version of Yourself
objectives_summary: Breaking Through Imposter Syndrome and Stepping into HERSTORY will help  guide you through exercises that will allow you to discover your strengths, passions and purpose. You'll gain access to tools needed to break through your own self-doubt, fear or other limiting beliefs that's holding you back from success and happiness. This course includes enlightening videos that will propel you to success, workbooks filled with action steps designed for reflection as well as personal journaling space so that once completed this program can serve as a guidebook for years to come.
